author: @trancedoutkid
text: Ok, let's get real nerdy real quick and talk about how often their super powers are being used throughout this choreography. Cause there's the obvious stuff like Kyungsoo and Suho using their abilities to control the others but there's subtle moments like how everyone's footwork practically stops when Xiumin takes over, they freeze in place and their moves immediately become sharp as ice. Or Sehun using his wind to transition the others between positions and in the final scene, to spin them all around him. Baekhyun not really controlling the others often but getting to shine like a light on his own when he is center. Chen hitting that high note and everyone reacting as if they're being struck by lightning but it's the bass. there's also a scene where Chanyeol spins around, as if he's thrown fire and Suho reacts as if he's using his water to stop it. ...these guys are literal perfection and this choreo is some of their best in my opinion.

author: @liza_pet
text: 많은 사람들이"크림 소다"를"러브 샷""몬스테트"와"코코 밥"과 비교하지만 나는 생각한다 모든 엑소 앨범은 이전 앨범과는 별개의 걸작입니다. 내 의견으로는 "크림 소다"는 엑소의 새로운 단계입니다. 결국,그들이 다시 한 번 자신의 놀라운 재능,무진장 한 잠재력,끝없는 성장 및 개발을 전문적인 수준에서 보여줌으로써 자신을 능가했다는 사실 외에도,다른 곳에서는 보일 것입니다.! 가장 중요한 것은,나는 완전히 다른,새로운 측면에서 각 멤버를 보았다,그들은 놀라게하고 내 영혼의 깊이에 나를 놀라게. 결론적으로,나는 한때 내 인생에서 엑소를 만난 것이 얼마나 기쁘다.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Many people compare "Cream Soda" with "Love Shot" "Monstet" and "Ko Ko Bop", but I think that absolutely every EXO album is a separate masterpiece unlike the previous one. In my opinion , "Cream Soda" is a new step for EXO. After all, apart from the fact that they once 
again surpassed themselves by showing their incredible talent, inexhaustible potential, endless growth and development at a professional level, although it would seem where else?! 
Most importantly, I saw each member from 
a completely different, new side, they amazed and surprised me to the depths of my soul. 
In conclusion, how glad I am that I once met 
EXO in my life.

author: @melonamelody17__
text:
EXO is a South Korean boy group that debuted on April 8 with the single 'Mama' which was then followed by 'EP Mama' on April 9.

The band consists of 9 members with the order of members from the oldest, Xiumin, Suho, Lay, Baekhyun, Chen, Chanyeol, D.O., Kai, and Sehun.

Since its debut, EXO has won many awards that make EXO's popularity never disappear from the per-kpop world.

author: @liza_pet
text:
Многие сравнивают "Cream Soda" с "Love Shot" "Monstet" и "Ko Ko Bop", но я считаю 
что абсолютно каждый альбом EXO это отдельный шедевр не похожий на предыдущий на мой взгляд именно 
"Cream Soda" является новой ступенью для EXO. Ведь помимо того что они в очередной раз превзошли сами себя показав свой невероятный талант, неиссекаемый потенциал, бесконечный рост и развитие на профессиональном уровне хотя казалось бы куда ещё?! Самое главное я увидела каждого мембера с совершенно другой–новой стороны они поразили и удивили меня до глубины души. 
В заключении как же сильно я рада что однажды встретила EXO в своей жизни.

text: They have that X factor that you won’t see in other groups who are known to be great at dancing. author: @triwidyaningsih11
text: Senang rasanya masih bisa melihat kalian eksis sampai sekarang sesuai album kalian kali ini.. Dlu kalian debut saya smp dan sedang down banget karena peringkat turun ditambah tekanan keluarga menuntut saya harus jdi ranking dan itu berbulan-bulan saya down 😭 tapi ketika exo debut saya seperti merasakan rasa semangat yg pernah hilang.. Hingga saat ini saya sudah lulus kuliah sarjana bebas skripsi bahkan awalnya saya sampai ada niatan kuliah di luar negeri terutama di korea, rasanya tidak bisa saya pungkiri karena asupan motivasi dari kalian.. Maaf terdengar berlebihan tapi mungkin dari kalian saya sangat merasakan bagaimana bertahan, berusaha dan selalu memacu diri untuk lebih baik, ditengah kesibukan kalian bertahan di industri kpop kalian masih mengutamakan pendidikan bahkan hingga pascasarjana. Saya berharap cita-cita saya bisa kuliah pascasarjana di luar negeri dapat terwujud kalaupun tidak di luar negeri di indonesia juga tidak papa, diluar negeri bukan untuk bertemu kalian tapi saya ingin lebih maju, tapi kalau bertemu juga saya bersyukur hehehe.. Stay health exo, im so proud of you 🕊🕊

text: "나는 2012년부터 팬이었습니다. 실망하거나 좌절한 적 없는 하루도 분도 순간도 없습니다. 항상 팬으로서 자랑스러웠으며 다른 누군가의 팬이 되기를 한 번도 바라지 않았습니다. 심지어 제 음악적 취향도 높아졌습니다. 다른 사람들의 음악을 들어도 같은 감정을 느끼지 않습니다. 내 귀는 여전히 당신을 갈망합니다. 당신은 이 세상에서 가치를 따져볼 수 없는 귀중한 보물입니다. 함께 하자고요. 정말 사랑합니다. 당신이 공연하고 열정을 가득 담아 표현할 때 세상이 손에 닿을 듯한 기분이 듭니다. 활동 중 건강에 신경 쓰시고 부상이나 질병에 걸리지 않도록 주의하세요. 너무 사랑합니다."

author: @liza_pet
text: Do Kyungsoo is just an incredible person that I will never stop admiring. At first glance, the album, the songs and his vocals may seem simple, but in fact it is not so at all. A large range does not make you a better vocalist yet, because another important role is played by the "technique", which Kyungsoo undoubtedly has great. He has such control over his voice that he makes all the transitions from low to high notes completely smoothly and even seems to make no effort. Quite naturally, during a song, it can change its timbre from incredibly sweet to sexually rude and sound simply amazing in each. Kyungsoo is one of those few vocalists who can make your heart flutter.

author: @キーウイ
text: デビューからのＰVをみてキレがあってかっこいいダンス、このCreamsodaで確信しました。１０年たってもEXOは進化しつづけていると。しなやかなダンスと歌😊メンバーが年齢を重ねてきて何て大人っぽいダンスをするんだと。ダンスが今までとは違う感覚です。何かホントに嬉しいです。私は41歳でEXOを知り、ダンスの衝撃と耳に残る歌声で毎日の生活が楽しくなりました。ライブ行きたいなあとか沢山夢を思うようになりました。ファンになって9年経った今、またあの時の気持ちになった気がして、これからもEXOと一緒に年を重ねていきます!応援しています😊ファンを大切に思ってくれて、ありがとう。メンバーの皆さんも自分の心のままにEXOとして、また唯一無二の自分自身として生きていく姿を見せてください。メンバーの皆さんが幸せだとファンの私達も幸せなのです。どうか怪我や体調に無理しないよう、それだけです。

author: @kytoo78
text:
Mes amis, je retombe amoureuse de ce groupe à chaque fois un peu plus fort!!
Je suis une EXO L dans le sang, les gens!!
La choré est trop addictive! Déjà que Cream Soda est un énième MASTERPIECE (tout l'album en est composé d'ailleurs), mais mon petit coeur ne tient pas quand Xiumin dit "Gimme that YumYum" et le hipthrust langoureux de BaekHyun à 2:23...
Bref, mon coeur va lâcher face à tant de mangnificience...
Mes oreilles et mes yeux sont en extase!!

Ce qui est cool, c'est que le Fandom devient de plus en plus clean! Il serait d'ailleurs intelligent pour nous, EXO-L , de ne plus prêter attention aux attaques de certains autres fandom! Nous sommes au dessus de ça désormais!
EXO, c'est le vin ou le champagne millésimé que seuls les connaisseurs peuvent apprécier à leur juste valeur!
Restons concentrés et faisons honneur au groupe par un comportement exemplaire!

Merci d'exister EXO!!!🙌🙌🙌❤❤❤❤

text:
Resep Teh Lemon Madu 
Bahan: 300 ml air
1 buah jeruk lemon
1 sdm daun teh hitam kering
2 sdm madu
Cara membuat: Potong separuh lemon, peras secukupnya.
Rebus air hingga mendidih.
Seduh daun teh kering dengan air panas.
Ambil parutan, parut bagian terluar kulit lemon ke dalam seduhan teh, jangan sampai terkena bagian putihnya karena pahit. Aduk rata.
Saring teh ke dalam gelas, tambahkan madu, aduk rata.
Nikmati teh hangat jeruk lemon madu yang segar dan cocok diminum kapan saja.
